Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:20.27,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,我军主力在威塞克斯击败了反抗势力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:25.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,镇压该地也只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:30.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,最快在冬天来临之前就能结束战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,伦敦之后怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说克努特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:40.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如今他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:41.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:45.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,克努特殿下率领的包围军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:50.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在被托鲁克尔部队击败后下落不明
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.96,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1015,1000)}                 Marlborough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息称他们在马尔伯勒与敌军交战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已经和当地部队合流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,至于殿下的安危  目前仍然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是余心疼的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么消息  马上告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是被围住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:30.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:35.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧  我都说了会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来  大伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  别射回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:47.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克诺克的使者们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,贵国的迎接有点粗暴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能说我们的语言啊  野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:01.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你们丹麦人是语言不通的畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把兵撤回  阿瑟尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,与丹麦人为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们威尔士毫无益处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉提安努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:17.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常敬佩你能为威尔士诸国的将来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:22.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我们的想法和你的有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能指望和丹麦王子做什么约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们终究是蛮族  不会和我们讲理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋在吼什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要不要开干  快说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不  打不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你听得懂吗  比约恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不  听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真想打的话  一开始就会射死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:54.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是想虚张声势  使谈判对自己更有利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:03.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直仔细观察你们和英格兰之间的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:08.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,十年间  你们三次和英格兰缔结休战协定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你们随后全都撕毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会重蹈英格兰的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要抓住王子来做我们的挡箭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是恶鬼之王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但必定很爱惜自己的继承人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  阿谢拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  反正是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,发发牢骚  看我们会有什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:37.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个时代  山羊不披着狼皮也吃不到草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很同情他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:43.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把你的计划告诉他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过既然他们想演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们配合一下他们也挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,站在这里的这位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正是丹麦国王斯韦恩陛下之子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,克努特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在殿下有话对你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下  请来一段震慑人心的演说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如「小心我把你们煮掉吃了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,向这些无礼的家伙表达下您的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要您说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就会吓到缩卵主动让路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下不喜欢在众人面前说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:57.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以  朗纳尔阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:58.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算年轻也好歹是一国的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他有自己应该履行的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在这里的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可都是为王子殿下而战的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:16.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下天性仁慈  不喜好无意义的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  这就是为了避免无意义的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,才让他出面震慑下局面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:25.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他像贝壳般一声不吭地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就能继承斯韦恩王的江山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:35.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们哪里懂得殿下的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:40.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,王宫是血亲之间骨肉相残的龙潭虎穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道当时体弱多病的殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:46.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在宫中受了多少苦才活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:52.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下韬光养晦  低调行事才活到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:56.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然而像你这样的鼠辈仍然不断出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:59.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,企图利用殿下而接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我搞清楚自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不论殿下要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没有资格插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在争什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,克努特王子说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉提安努斯阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把计划告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙们  在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去和他们的老大谈几句
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,朗纳尔阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我因为太过担心殿下的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心说了些出格的言论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还请殿下恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真逊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的和我一样大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男的  名字叫朗纳尔对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:41.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他不知道雏鸟总有一天要离巢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样反而对雏鸟不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:55.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了完成计划  你要做的事情好像有点多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是让雏鸟离巢么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.28,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,退下  我不需要护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我说第二遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让他们觉得没有卫兵保护就不敢来谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我岂不成了王家的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,走到离这里五倍远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:35.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也告诉其他人一声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你叫阿谢拉特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是不清楚你们的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可这实际上让我们很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你们不是谈妥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:56.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们突然来信希望我们准许过境并且提供兵粮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们没法答应这两点要求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我国弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们王家也是要面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们给你们提供方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:09.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能得到什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:13.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我得确认这是一场对等的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:19.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让平民觉得国王连区区一百个丹麦人都不敢对付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果直接答应了我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有损贵国的颜面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对此我考虑不周 还请见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:34.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,寄给贵国的书信是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过信里应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬不详述是为了保证机密不泄露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就谈谈这个机密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以先问一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我提到的报酬不合心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有没可能招致战斗呢  阿瑟尔阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样为难我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很清楚要是惹怒了丹麦王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小国就根本活不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我只是确认一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问  肯定是阿谢拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道他会说威尔士语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:33.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在队里待最久的你也有不知道的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么  不知道的多了去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要说我知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:41.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只知道他是丹麦人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个薄情的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起打拼了十几年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  这么大块头还闹别扭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好烦啊  要打架的话随时奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个好首领
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,运气又好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能带着我赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:06.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论他身世如何  我都会跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一时事出突然有些难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 又不像在说谎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是直系血统的莉迪娅大人之子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这位阿谢拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:31.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,继承了我们罗马·凯尔特伟大领袖的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:36.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  阁下不是丹麦人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是威尔士与丹麦的混血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲沃拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经在掠夺威尔士沿海时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:46.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,将莉迪娅掳为爱妾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后生下了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:55.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说古不列颠尼亚军神的血脉已经断绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:01.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下居然是阿托利斯的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿托利斯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.14,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}Artorius
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:09.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,活跃于5至6世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:14.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,英国原住民凯尔特人的国家·不列颠尼亚的军团总指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,公元516年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,面对进攻势如破竹的撒克逊人军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,即后来所称呼的英格兰人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他率军于巴登山之战将其击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:28.57,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,为不列颠尼亚带来了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:36.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他的故事为后世传颂  成为亚瑟王传说的人物原型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:36.14,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：以上历史较早记叙于《不列颠人的历史》，\N据传为9世纪时期的威尔士僧侣所著史书，内容真实性尚有争议。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下所讲述的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有足以令人信服的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以证明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人在十四岁时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,和莉迪娅大人一起来到威尔士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我第一次遇见他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲的一生非常不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,常年被软禁在父亲的寝室里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:10.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,得病以后就被抛弃到马厩里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,实在可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:19.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  伟大血脉的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是和丹麦的混血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,关键就在这  阿瑟尔阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为是混血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能融入丹麦人的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说威尔士在丹麦军队里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:37.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有了我这么一个间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能将那个小少爷拥立为下任丹麦王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也将能担任足以左右国政的要职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:51.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让丹麦缔结对威尔士的互不侵犯条约
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:16:01.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不让那帮家伙踏入这片土地一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,诚惶诚恐  何等大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有如此之大的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瑟尔大人在笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是位有胆魄的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在丹麦人之中长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:33.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,与丹麦的血统比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能一直更倾向于认同阿托利斯的血统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这方面只能信不信由你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算抛开血统的问题不说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:55.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌丹麦人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剑放到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:00.48,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.02,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,要完好无损地还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:04.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要交出武器  简直不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在通过这个国家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:15.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,装作是他们俘虏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我们遣送到国境之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就会把武器还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来他们的颜面就保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:30.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你的部下都对你言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也好  我可是深得部下信赖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  托尔芬  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑  秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:42.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,深得信赖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是例外  臭小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要误会了  尖脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个秃头的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:53.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就两个人的话应该不会计较
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:05.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好  继续进军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,丹麦人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瑟尔大人好像俘虏了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.21,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,听说会吃人肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.34,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,好吓人  一副恶人嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:27.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有长角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是阿瑟尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不扔块石头试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这群人真是令人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们当奇珍异兽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么看  臭章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么呢  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想说话就用你的嘴说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.28,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没长舌头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:18.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是因为胆小才不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:19.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是因为我要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说话必须慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,和…和你们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.01,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:37.00,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听到他的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:37.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的发言是有政治意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况现在身处外国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,未经父王陛下的允许
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:47.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自签订互不侵犯条约  或者表现愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能随便做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我很慎重的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这辩解得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还是有点脑子嘛  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你个无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,从来就没有人敢以这个态度对我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是一次挺好的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,收回你的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我这不是辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种人怎么会明白王族的辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那叫嚷了  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有乱叫嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在主张我个人发言的正确性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你这是什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:42.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下居然跟我以外的人说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.84,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,把我当成什么人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.67,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,作为侍从太无礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.59,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想成为你的侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿谢拉特  不能再快一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去会被大雪困住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 好烦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.01,0:21:49.81,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(910,1000)}        Mercia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:49.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们横跨麦西亚伯爵领地北端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:52.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再向大本营根斯堡进发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:54.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,最快一周内到达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要在敌人的领地内前进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:00.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在威尔士的山间被雪困住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:08.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,距离敌人的大本营也很远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  兵粮要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,地方领主怎么可能会向丹麦人提供帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:16.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个也考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙们  调整方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:29.64,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.28,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变道？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:32.34,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:36.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心  阿谢拉特的判断不会出错
